OL,5,C'problematic' ` ASA
OL,7,FThe ad, seen in June, included a
OL,8,Fvoiceover that said: "To those who
OL,9,Fmight scratch day and night. To those
OL,10,Fwhose skin will feel dried out even by
OL,11,Fwater," alongside scenes of a black
OL,12,Fwoman with red scratch marks and
OL,13,Fanother covered with a cracked clay-
OL,14,Flike material.
OL,16,FAlongside scenes of a white woman
OL,17,Ftaking a shower with the product, the
OL,18,Fad then stated: "Try to take a shower
OL,19,Fwith the new Sanex skin therapy and
OL,20,Fits patented amino acid complex. For
OL,21,F24 hour hydration feel."
