OL,7,FThe ad ended with on-screen text and
OL,8,Fthe voiceover stating: "Relief could
OL,9,Fbe as simple as a shower."
OL,11,FColgate-Palmolive, which owns the
OL,12,FSanex brand, said the depiction of
OL,13,Fdiverse models in the ad, either
OL,14,Fexperiencing skin discomfort or post-
OL,15,Fproduct relief, was shown in a "before
OL,16,Fand after" scenario to show their
OL,17,Fproduct was suitable and effective for
OL,18,Fall, rather than as a comparison based
OL,19,Fon race or ethnicity.
