OL,7,FThe agency said one model with darker
OL,8,Fskin was depicted in a "stylised and
OL,9,Funrealistic way" to demonstrate
OL,10,Fdryness, but her skin tone was
OL,11,Fotherwise not a focal point.
OL,13,FA second model, also with darker skin,
OL,14,Fwas shown with itchy skin, but this
OL,15,Fwas portrayed through scratching
OL,16,Fvisibly healthy skin and the resulting
OL,17,Fmarks, and was therefore more about
OL,18,Fsensation than any visible skin
OL,19,Fcondition.
