OL,7,FThe watchdog said: "The ad was
OL,8,Ftherefore structured in such a way
OL,9,Fthat it was the black skin, depicted
OL,10,Fin association with itchy and dry
OL,11,Fskin, which was shown to be
OL,12,Fproblematic and uncomfortable, whereas
OL,13,Fthe white skin, depicted as smoother
OL,14,Fand clean after using the product, was
OL,15,Fshown successfully changed and
OL,16,Fresolved.
OL,18,F"We considered that could be
OL,19,Finterpreted as suggesting that white
OL,20,Fskin was superior to black skin."
